stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> Unregistered : initialize()
    Unregistered --> Registered : register(task_id)<br/>copy name + threshold<br/>seed snapshot
    Registered --> Healthy : start()<br/>sync snapshot<br/>clear miss counter
    Healthy --> Warning : 1 missed cycle<br/>(grace period)
    Warning --> Healthy : counter advances
    Warning --> Timeout : miss count >= threshold
    Timeout --> Healthy : counter advances again<br/>(re-arms one-shot alarm)
    Healthy --> Inactive : deactivate()<br/>pauses evaluation
    Inactive --> Healthy : activate()<br/>re-syncs snapshot
    Registered --> Unregistered : unregister()
    Healthy --> Unregistered : unregister()
